description:
Legendary impressionist & comedian Frank Caliendo can become Morgan Freeman, John Madden, Donald Trump, Bill Clinton, Alex Jones and more. He’s impressed most of the Avengers, was gifted a diamond watch by Donald Trump and has a daughter that warned him about coming on IMPAULSIVE; maybe because Dan Bilzerian hates Big Mike? Or Logan has deceptive and manipulative eyes? Find out in today’s episode...
